<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Görg, als wir ew vormals
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>embot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>sünderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nehst <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Niclas Muffels,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewte
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, darauf uns noch kein lawter antwurt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist,
                        ob <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> arm lewt vor ew sicher sein
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht; das uns fremd nymt und
                        unczeitlich <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew dunkt.
                            <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> als ir schreibt und maint, ew und den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> süll
                            <expan>ungütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein, nu maint der unser, es sey seinen
                        armen <expan>lewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und gescheh in
                            <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew noch ungütlich, daz sie
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew <add>auf recht</add> nicht gesichert
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> künnen. Und ob ew nu
                        <add>dewht</add>, daz ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> von den seinen iht unpillichs
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>varen</expan> wer, darumb wil
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> unser
                            <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> ew, den
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen
                        gewalt <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den seinen</add> frewntlichs
                                <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen, wenn er des ermant wirdt
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wir
                                <expan>bit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir uns bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brief
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lawter wissen
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, ob des
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> armen lewte darauf <add>vor ew</add>
                        sicher sein <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht, daz wir und
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> unser uns darnach gen ew cze
                                <expan>richt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan>
<expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan>.</ab>
